this property, I was mortified,

00:17:00.690 --> 00:17:01.960
embarrassed.

00:17:01.960 --> 00:17:04.355
I mean, I considered
myself well-read

00:17:04.355 --> 00:17:06.450
and I couldn't believe I
didn't know this story.

