I just started with a show

00:18:00.760 --> 00:18:02.140
last year.

00:18:02.140 --> 00:18:04.890
Some people have been with
it much longer than that.

00:18:04.890 --> 00:18:08.100
But I auditioned for the show
and I didn't know anything

00:18:08.100 --> 00:18:09.130
about John Newton.

00:18:09.130 --> 00:18:11.520
I read the script and
I was like, oh wow,

00:18:11.520 --> 00:18:14.170
they really made a really
cool dramatic story.

00:18:14.170 --> 00:18:15.520
This can't possibly be true.

00:18:15.520 --> 00:18:16.815
And it's real.

00:18:16.815 --> 00:18:18.700
I was like this is
stranger than fiction.

00:18:18.700 --> 00:18:19.930
I spoke to the
director on the phone

00:18:19.930 --> 00:18:22.096
and I remember asking him,
how much of this is true?

00:18:22.096 --> 00:18:24.560
And he's like--
there's this character,

00:18:24.560 --> 00:18:25.560
this princess character.

00:18:25.560 --> 00:18:26.768
I was like, oh she's made up.

00:18:26.768 --> 00:18:27.620
No, she's not.

00:18:27.620 --> 00:18:28.790
She's real.

00:18:28.790 --> 00:18:29.680
I was like, wow!

00:18:29.680 --> 00:18:34.849
I couldn't believe just how
incredible, truly, stranger

00:18:34.849 --> 00:18:35.890
than fiction his life is.

00:18:35.890 --> 00:18:38.040
I mean, he was a
slave trader, who

00:18:38.040 --> 00:18:39.597
was then enslaved
and then became

00:18:39.597 --> 00:18:41.180
a leader of the
abolitionist movement.

00:18:41.180 --> 00:18:42.300
CAROLYN ROSSI COPELAND:
And branded a slave.

00:18:42.300 --> 00:18:43.341
ERIN MACKEY: And branded.

00:18:43.341 --> 00:18:45.680
I mean, it's just incredible.

00:18:45.680 --> 00:18:49.000
So I knew nothing,
and then I've learned.

